name: spells
description: spells are often misportrayed in movies as weaponized abilities used to duel enemies, likely due to the fact that cgi drenched action scenes sell tickets. in reality, the vast majority of spells are cast to transmit love, luck, and other benevolent enchantments from person to person. though some use spells to cause mischief and misery, this approach is much less popular as curses rarely work as intended. cast to invoke generosity. inscribed by tenorless circa 2021 // elements collection [fire]
